More complex procedural logic: hull and traversal must update dynamically as modules are added\par
\par
AI and drone logistics must handle changing interior networks\par
\par
Must handle recomputing density fields / isosurface hulls incrementally\par
\par
Potential complexity in symmetry and alignment as modules are attached\par
\par
Might need module attachment rules to prevent weird or invalid layouts\par
\par
\f2 3\u-497?\f3\u8419?\f0  Hybrid Approach\par
You could combine both methods:\par
