NovaForge Full Scene Live Editing Workflow\par
Step\tab Action\tab Asset Types\tab ToolingLayer / UI\tab DeltaEdits Behavior\tab Notes\par
1\tab Spawn Player & Scene\tab Characters, Ships, Hangar, Props\tab ToolingLayer disabled\tab N/A\tab Loads baseline PCG + any saved DeltaEdits. Player spawns in hangar with ship.\par
2\tab Pause Gameplay / Detach Items\tab Characters, Equipment, Modules\tab N/A\tab Objects enter hover/edit mode\tab Everything equipped or attached detaches and hovers near player for editing.\par
3\tab Open ToolingLayer UI\tab All editable assets\tab Selection Panel: pick asset\tab N/A\tab UI overlays scene for live editing. Categories filter assets: Characters, Ships, Modules, Props, Hangar.\par
4\tab Select Asset / Category\tab Ships, Modules, Props, Hangar, Character\tab Selection Panel\tab N/A\tab Highlights asset in 3D scene; gizmos appear for manipulation.\par
5\tab Edit Transform / Placement\tab Ships, Modules, Props, Hangar\tab Gizmos: move, rotate, scale\tab DeltaEdits records position & rotation changes\tab Snap to grid / align options available.\par
6\tab Assign Functions / Behaviors\tab Ships modules, Props, Hangar doors/consoles\tab Function Panel\tab DeltaEdits stores function assignments\tab Examples: Auto-Fire, Flicker Lights, Trigger Spawn.\par
7\tab Edit Physics / Procedural Parameters\tab Clothing, Capes, Rigs, Animations\tab Physics Panel + Environment Presets Panel\tab DeltaEdits stores updated physics & environment presets\tab Adjust stiffness, damping, drag, gravity influence.\par
8\tab Live Preview / Simulation\tab All edited assets\tab Live Preview Panel: Play / Pause / Scrub / Move Character\tab Changes reflected immediately in 3D scene\tab Can test animations, ship module movement, prop interactions, environment effects.\par
9\tab Test Interactions\tab Ships, Props, Hangar, Characters\tab Live Preview + Function Panel\tab Updates DeltaEdits on function test (optional)\tab Trigger assigned behaviors; spawn AI-generated assets for testing.\par
10\tab Apply / Commit DeltaEdits\tab All modified assets\tab DeltaEdits Panel: Save / Assign to PCG Baseline\tab Saves modifications to persistent storage\tab All changes will influence future PCG generation.\par
11\tab Close ToolingLayer / Resume Gameplay\tab Entire Scene\tab N/A\tab Edits applied in live world\tab All assets now reflect new positions, functions, physics, and animations.\par
12\tab PCG Regeneration / Next Pull\tab Characters, Ships, Hangar, Props\tab N/A\tab DeltaEdits applied automatically\tab Scene regenerates respecting edits for new procedural worlds.\par
