Perfect\f6  \f4\emdash  let\rquote s lay out the exact initialization sequence for RuntimeBootstrap \u8594? ToolingLayer \u8594? DevWorld, ensuring the system loads cleanly, all dependencies are resolved, and the live editor overlay can safely interact with all Dev World assets.\par
\par
This will also highlight how PCG, DeltaTracker, Hangars, and Blueprint nodes hook in.\par
\par
1. Initialization Sequence Overview\par
RuntimeBootstrap (core startup)\par
 \u9492?\u9472?> Core Systems (Logging, Config, ECS, Assets)\par
      \u9492?\u9472?> Runtime Systems (Simulation, World, Physics)\par
           \u9492?\u9472?> ToolingLayer Overlay (F12 toggle)\par
                \u9492?\u9472?> DevWorld (Hangars, Rooms, Fleet, Planets)\par
                     \u9500?\u9472?> DeltaTracker\par
                     \u9500?\u9472?> PCGPreview\par
                     \u9500?\u9472?> PCGStyleCompiler\par
                     \u9492?\u9472?> BlueprintSystem\par
2. Step-by-Step Loading Order\par
Step 1: RuntimeBootstrap\par
Purpose: Unified boot logic for Game/Editor/Server; no duplicate startup code.\par
\par
Actions:\par
\par
Initialize Core systems:\par
\par
Logging\par
\par
Config files\par
\par
ECS registry\par
\par
Asset registry (models, textures, JSON templates)\par
\par
Initialize Runtime systems:\par
\par
Simulation tick scheduler\par
\par
Physics engine\par
\par
World loader (empty scene at first)\par
\par
Setup networking if client/server mode\par
\par
void RuntimeBootstrap::Initialize()\par
\{\par
    Core::InitLogging();\par
    Core::LoadConfigFiles();\par
    ECS::RegisterComponents();\par
    Assets::LoadBaseAssets();\par
\par
    Runtime::InitSimulation();\par
    Runtime::InitPhysics();\par
    Runtime::LoadEmptyWorld();\par
\}\par
Step 2: ToolingLayer Overlay\par
Purpose: Editor UI overlay ready before any live world content is loaded.\par
\par
Actions:\par
\par
Initialize Panels:\par
\par
ShipEditor, ModuleEditor, HangarEditor, NPCEditor, DialogueEditor, BlueprintEditor\par
\par
Initialize Gizmos:\par
\par
SelectionSystem, Transform/Rotate/Scale gizmos\par
\par
Set up Input Bindings:\par
\par
F12 toggle overlay\par
\par
Mouse/keyboard mapping\par
\par
Hook into ECS/DeltaTracker for live edit recording\par
\par
Subscribe to entity spawn events for real-time updates\par
\par
void ToolingLayer::Initialize()\par
\{\par
    Panels::InitAll();\par
    Gizmos::InitAll();\par
    Input::BindKey(F12, ToggleOverlay);\par
    DeltaTracker::Subscribe(this); // record edits\par
\}\par
Step 3: DevWorld / DevStation\par
Purpose: Load editable test solar system with hangars, ships, rooms, planets.\par
\par
Actions:\par
\par
Load rooms and hangars (Small \u8594? XXL)\par
\par
Spawn fleet ships in each hangar using ECS/EntityFactory\par
\par
Apply any saved DeltaEdits for ships, modules, interiors, planets\par
\par
Initialize TodoList for each room/hangar\par
\par
Hook PCGPreview and PCGStyleCompiler for live propagation\par
\par
Load NPCs and Blueprint nodes in rooms\par
\par
Notify ToolingLayer that entities are ready for live editing\par
\par
void DevWorld::Initialize()\par
\{\par
    DevStation::LoadRooms();\par
    DevStation::SpawnFleetShips();\par
    DeltaTracker::ApplyDeltas();\par
    TodoList::InitAllRooms();\par
    PCGPreview::RefreshScene();\par
    PCGStyleCompiler::InitTemplates();\par
    BlueprintGraph::InitAll();\par
    ToolingLayer::OnDevWorldReady();\par
\}\par
3. Live Editing Hook Integration\par
Once initialized:\par
\par
F12 \u8594? ToolingLayer overlay active\par
\par
Entity selection \u8594? via Raycast/SelectionSystem\par
\par
Transform/module edits \u8594? recorded in DeltaTracker\par
\par
Blueprint nodes \u8594? execute connected actions (NPC spawn, module attach, regenerate PCG)\par
\par
PCGPreview \u8594? live updates the DevWorld scene\par
\par
Hangar completion \u8594? triggers style propagation across fleet hangars\par
\par
Planets/world \u8594? optional edits applied via same DeltaTracker \u8594? style templates\par
\par
4. Notes / Considerations\par
Dependencies:\par
\par
ToolingLayer must initialize before any DevWorld entity edits.\par
\par
DevWorld must initialize after ToolingLayer to allow hooks for Gizmos and Panels.\par
\par
DeltaTracker: Central hub for all live edits \u8594? must exist before DevWorld entities spawn.\par
\par
PCGStyleCompiler: Can be initialized early, but final templates are applied after DeltaEdits are loaded.\par
\par
BlueprintGraph: Nodes can reference entities; must be initialized after DevWorld spawns entities but before overlay usage.\par
\par
Input Bindings: Overlay toggle and gizmos must be active after RuntimeBootstrap and before first frame.\par
\par
5. Full Initialization Timeline (Frame 0)\par
Frame 0:\par
\u9500?\u9472?\u9472? RuntimeBootstrap::Initialize()\par
\u9474?    \u9492?\u9472?\u9472? Core + Runtime systems ready\par
\u9500?\u9472?\u9472? ToolingLayer::Initialize()\par
\u9474?    \u9492?\u9472?\u9472? Panels, Gizmos, Input, DeltaTracker hooks\par
\u9500?\u9472?\u9472? DevWorld::Initialize()\par
\u9474?    \u9500?\u9472?\u9472? Rooms, Hangars, Ships, Planets loaded\par
\u9474?    \u9500?\u9472?\u9472? DeltaEdits applied\par
\u9474?    \u9500?\u9472?\u9472? TodoLists ready\par
\u9474?    \u9500?\u9472?\u9472? Blueprint nodes initialized\par
\u9474?    \u9492?\u9472?\u9472? PCGPreview / PCGStyleCompiler hooked\par
\u9492?\u9472?\u9472? Live gameplay/editor loop begins\par
Outcome:\par
\par
Player can immediately toggle ToolingLayer overlay\par
\par
Select and edit entities (ships, modules, interiors, NPCs)\par
\par
Changes recorded and propagated via DeltaTracker + PCGStyleCompiler\par
\par
Blueprint nodes drive dynamic actions and PCG regeneration\par
\par
Fleet hangars and planetary templates respond to edits in real-time\par
\par
