\par
1.1 Influence Channels\par
Players affect style via:\par
\par
\f7\bullet  \f6 Visitation frequency\par
\f7\bullet  \f6 Time spent in system types\par
\f7\bullet  \f6 Combat density\par
\f7\bullet  \f6 Trade volume\par
\f7\bullet  \f6 Base-building density\par
\f7\bullet  \f6 Ship class usage\par
\f7\bullet  \f6 Planet settlement patterns\par
