\par
1.2 Aggregation Model\par
For each system type S:\par
\par
engagementScore(S) =\par
    weightedSum(\par
        visits,\par
        dwellTime,\par
        transactions,\par
        battles,\par
        constructions\par
    )\par
Normalize:\par
\par
engagementNormalized(S) =\par
    engagementScore(S) / maxAcrossAllTypes\par
