\par
Gizmos and panels can directly manipulate entities during FPS/EVA/Ship movement.\par
\par
BlueprintGraph execution:\par
\par
Each tick, executes nodes tied to player actions (enter room, dock ship, complete tasks).\par
\par
Can spawn NPCs, attach modules, or trigger PCG regeneration dynamically.\par
\par
Mode switching:\par
\par
FPS \f7\u8594? \f6 EVA \f7\u8594? \f6 Ship is seamless; controllers are modular.\par
\par
Physics solver adapts automatically (gravity on stations, zero-G in EVA/space).\par
