Integration Notes\par
Hangars / Rooms:\par
\par
Each hangar contains fleet slots; each slot has a ship entity.\par
\par
Rooms track all entities (ships, modules, NPCs, props) and have todo lists for developer workflow.\par
\par
Completing a room/hangar triggers PCGStyleCompiler propagation.\par
\par
DeltaTracker:\par
\par
Each Hangar, Room, and Ship has a pointer to DeltaTracker for recording edits.\par
\par
DeltaEdits are applied immediately for live preview and stored for persistent PCG influence.\par
\par
Fleet Propagation:\par
\par
When a hangar or ship edit is completed, PropagateStyleToFleet() updates all relevant fleet hangars.\par
\par
Modular garage slots allow fleet expansion without breaking PCG style.\par
\par
PlayerController Integration:\par
\par
When player is in FPS/EVA/Ship mode, edits to ships/modules/props are recorded in DeltaTracker automatically.\par
\par
ApplyDeltaEdits() can be called on entering/exiting hangar to ensure live preview and PCG propagation.\par
\par
TodoList:\par
\par
Tracks tasks for each room (e.g., \f7\ldblquote\f6 Edit Ship Hull #12\f7\rdblquote\f6 , \f7\ldblquote\f6 Fix NPC animation\f7\rdblquote\f6 ).\par
\par
Room completion triggers style propagation and fleet template update.\par
