Interaction Flow\par
Press TAB \f7\u8594? \f6 Opens Rig System GUI.\par
\par
Select Tab: Equipment, Inventory, or Crafting.\par
\par
Equipment Tab:\par
\par
Drag items from Inventory to Equipment slots.\par
\par
View real-time stats updates.\par
\par
Upgrade modules on slots if available.\par
\par
Inventory Tab:\par
\par
Drag items to Equipment slots or Crafting tab.\par
\par
Sort/filter items by type, weight, or rarity.\par
\par
Crafting Tab (if Assembler equipped):\par
\par
Drag ingredients into recipe slots.\par
\par
Press Quick Craft or Craft button to produce items.\par
\par
Exit GUI: Press TAB again.\par
\par
