Hover Tooltips \f7\u8594? \f6 Show stats, bonuses, upgrade slots, requirements.\par
\par
Drag-and-Drop Feedback \f7\u8594? \f6 Highlight valid slots.\par
\par
Visual Preview Panel \f7\u8594? \f6 Character rig shows equipped items live.\par
\par
Dynamic Crafting Updates \f7\u8594? \f6 Recipes appear/disappear based on inventory content.\par
